metadata.name: Black Card
metadata.description: 333 Limited-Edition Black Card Priority Passes for early GCC Black Card holders (OG Blackcard holders). The Black Card Priority Pass NFT unlocks premium privileges, such as priority/presale access to mint upcoming collections, and can also be used in future exclusive raffles to increase chances of winning more rewards.  The Global Citizen Club (GCC) is an elite luxury lifestyle Club with unique NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain, with a current collection of 8,888 Genesis Gentlemen Edition NFTs.
